Jim wrote:

> Does anyone have a disused one.  You know, just taking up space in the
> garage or shed.  I have a floor stand, just need the 'hooks to
> engine' part.

Go to your local salvage yard a pick up a bus bell housing.  Bolts right to
your stand, and if you're lucky and have the right size flywheel, you'll be
able to start and run the engine on the stand.
